short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save old tabs for later and free up memory

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save extra tabs for later to prevent them from eating up extra system resources. TabSaver reduces the amount of memory that Chrome needs by saving tabs for later use. It is lightweight, easy to use, and simple to save and restore tabs.
